m Band der Frage nachgegangen, was den Menschen auszeichnet. Die allgemeinverständlichen Beiträge von Dagmar Fenner, Annemarie Pieper, Wilhelm Schmid und Dieter Thomä widerstehen dabei der Verführung, endgültige Antworten geben zu wollen, sondern regen zur Selbstreflexion an.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aEthics. 0aHuman beings. 0aPhilosophical anthropology. 4aLebenskunst. 4aMensch. 4aMoral. 4aPhilosophie der Lebenskunst. 4aPhilosophie. 4aPhilosophische Anthropologie. 4aWerte. 7aPHILOSOPHY / General.2bisacsh  aArt of Living.  aHuman.  aPhilosophical Anthropology.  aPhilosophy As the Art of Living.  aPhilosophy.  aValues.1 aFenner, Dagmar, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKressig, Marcel Meier, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLindenau, Mathias, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLindenau, Mathias, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMeier Kressig, Marcel, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aPieper, Annemarie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchmid, Wilhelm, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aThomä, Dieter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Philosophy 2015z9783110438680oZDB-23-DPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839430323zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter